title: Undercover Blues (1993) Dennis Quaid (Widescr.Opt. MULTISUBS)

Optional subtitles in separate idx/sub files:
Danish, Dutch, English, Finnish, French, German, Greek, Italian, Norwegian, Spanish, Swedish

One of my first favourite action comedies about a couple on maternity "leave" from their jobs as secret agents.

Widescreen XviD 2-pass 720x400, great stereo AC3.
Burn tested, runs well in both my standalone DivX players.
